{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to integrating personalized formative feedback for students, the inclusion of such platforms in teachers' technological toolkit provides invaluable resources to augment their instructional practices.",
    "The deployment of this technology has the potential to liberate teachers' time, enabling them to concentrate on other crucial facets of teaching, all while delivering personalized, targeted support.",
    "LEAP also serves as a valuable platform for conducting empirical studies by enabling educators and researchers to efficiently extract and analyze data, providing valuable insights into the effectiveness of AI-driven feedback.",
    "This does not only facilitate academic research but also offers teachers valuable insights into how students interact with the content.",
    "These insights can guide interventions or adjustments to the prompting strategy, thereby enhancing the effectiveness of the learning process."
  ]
}